title: Watch Dogs Update v1.03.471-RELOADED
description:

Note:

You do not need any other updates for this release. All available DLC
content is unlocked. Check the included .txt file for a list of what's new.

1. Unrar.
2. Install the update EXACTLY to the dir where main game is installed.
3. Copy over the cracked content from the /Crack directory to your game

4. Play the game.
5. Support the software developers. If you like this game, BUY IT!
